      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just one ear though, i feel like if it was actually serious it would bother both of them. i've had this kind of ringing in my ears before after a loud concert and it went away in a couple days. do you think maybe i just pushed some wax in there? i really don't want to spend money on a specialist if i can just wait it out for a bit.",
