      "content": "i get what you're saying but honestly i'm pretty sure i'm fine. i'll just try using some of those over the counter earwax removal drops tonight and see if it clears up by tomorrow. if i can just melt the wax away i wont have to deal with the doc. do you think those drops are usually pretty effective for stuff like this?",
